<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Mahajanganella gen. nov., scanning electron micrographs. Specimens used for imaging: A M. fridakahloae sp. nov. female paratype (ZMH-A 0016709); B, C M. schwarzeneggeri sp. nov. male paratype (ZMH-A 0016717). A carapace, dorsal; B sternum ventral; C coxal spines (highlighted in red). Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A, B); 0.1 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782004" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Drawings of Mahajanganella heraclis sp. nov.: A carapace from dorsal; B leg IV; C left chela from dorsal with trichobothrial pattern; D right pedipalp from dorsal. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A - C); 0.4 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782006" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure15>
    dc:description "Figure 15. Drawings of Mahajanganella fridakahloae sp. nov.: A carapace from dorsal; B leg IV; C left chela from dorsal with trichobothrial pattern; D right pedipalp from dorsal. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A - C); 0.4 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782007" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure16>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Drawings of Mahajanganella schwarzeneggeri sp. nov.: A carapace from dorsal; B leg IV; C left chela from dorsal with trichobothrial pattern; D right pedipalp from dorsal. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A - C); 0.4 mm (D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782008" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure11>
    dc:description "Figure 11. Mahajanganella gen. nov., habitus. Specimen used for imaging: M. schwarzeneggeri sp. nov. allotype (ZMH-A 0016716). A dorsal; B ventral; C lateral. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782003" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/asp.80.e90570.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Mahajanganella gen. nov., scanning electron micrographs. Specimens used for imaging: A M. heraclis sp. nov. male paratype (ZMH-A 0016701); B M. fridakahloae sp. nov. male paratype (ZMH-A 0016715); C M. schwarzeneggeri sp. nov. male paratype (ZMH-A 0016717). A right chela from ventral with specialized setae in a group in detail (highlighted in red); B left chela with double trichobothrium dt in detail (highlighted in red); C left chela from medial with terminal teeth in a compact group in detail. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/782005" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

